citation: Proclamation under the Pharmacists Registration Act 2001 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Pharmacists Registration Act 2001

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Pharmacists Registration Act 2001 fix 1 April 2002 as the day on which that Act commences.

18 March 2002

G. S. M. Green

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

Judy Jackson

Minister for Health and Human Services

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 27 March 2002

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
